scene.message:
Yukino: I thought the numbers{nl}
seemed low, and here they{nl}
are in a place like this...{waitkey}{clearbox}Hang on, everyone! We'll save{nl}
you soon!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: They still seem to be{nl}
breathing.{waitkey}The Eternal Night... so this{nl}
is what it meant.{waitkey}{ret}
